                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;OBJECT_UPDATE_PER_RPC_MAX is a internal to OUT&apos;s implementation limit. OUT can use RPC directly instead of copying arguments into env. OUT just needs to maintain resizable array of object pointers.&lt;br/&gt;
